<div id="accordion2" class="accordion">

      <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                  <span class="title">How can I find people or brands?</span>
                  <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content options">
            	<p>There are a number of ways to discover interesting people and brands:</p>

            	<ul>
            		<li>
            			<strong>Start Searching</strong> Use the search input in the top menu to find people or brands directly by their names, usernames, locations, or pursuits.
            		</li>
            		<li>
            			<strong>Browse Posts</strong> Browsing pages (such as media, projects, market, events, etc.) is a great way to discover things that may interest you. Which in turn can lead you to some great people/brands to follow. 
            		</li>
            		<li>
            			<strong>Discover Page</strong> Browsing the discover page directly (compass icon once logged in) is another great way to find people/brands. You can also browse the most popular pursuits and locations there. 
            		</li>
            		<li>
            			<strong>All of the above.</strong>
            		</li>
            	</ul>
            </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                  <span class="title">How do I follow others?</span>
                  <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
            	<p>Following another person or brand is as easy as going to their profiles and clicking on the follow button (the silhouette with the plus next to it) or by clicking the follow button on another page they may be listed on, such as the discover page.</p>
            </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                  <span class="title">How can I communicate with them?</span>
                  <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
            	<p>Commenting on a status, media, event, project, listing, etc. notifies the owner that you have left them a comment. You can also start a conversation with up to 14 others by the conversations link located in the top menu or on profile pages.</p>

                  <p>You can also mention another user in a number of different places. Typing @ followed by their username (i.e. @llfofficial), will send them a notification.</p>
            </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
            <div class="accordion-header">
                  <span class="title">Tips & Tricks</span>
                  <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content">
            	<ul>
            		<li>
            			Having a complete profile increases your visibility dramatically.
            		</li>
            		<li>
            			Searching pursuits is the best way to find people/brands that share your interests.
            		</li>
            		<li>
            			Check the newsticker for the latest news dealing with the culture and creativity!
            		</li>
            		<li>
            			The discover page displays random members of the community.
            		</li>
            	</ul>
            </div>
      </div>
      
</div>